quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  98,8,un ka sila un ke perwar-digaar ke haan hamesha rehne ke baagh hain jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain abad al abaad un mein rahen ge. khuda un se khush aur woh is se khush. yeh ( sila ) is ke liye hai jo apne perwar-digaar se darta raha
  99,1,jab zameen bhonchal se hila di jaye gi
  99,2,aur zameen apne ( andar ) ke boojh nikaal daaley gi
  99,3,aur ensaan kahe ga ke is kokiya howa hai ?
  99,4,is roz woh apne halaat bayan kardey gi
  99,5,kyunkay tumahray perwar-digaar ne is ko hukum bheja ( hoga )
  99,6,is din log giroh giroh ho kar ayen ge taakay un ko un ke aamaal dikha diye jayen
  99,7,to jis ne zarra bhar neki ki ho gi woh is ko dekh le ga
  99,8,aur jis ne zarra bhar buraiee ki hogi woh usay dekh le ga
  100,1,un sarpat dornay walay ghoron ki qasam jo haanp uthte hain
  100,2,phir ( patharon par na-al ) maar kar aag nikaltay hain
  100,3,phir subah ko chhapa maartay hain
  100,4,phir is mein gird uthatay hain
  100,5,phir is waqt dushman ki fouj mein ja gustay hain
  100,6,ke ensaan apne perwar-digaar ka ahsaan nashnas ( aur nashukara ) hai
  100,7,aur woh is se aagah bhi hai
  100,8,woh to maal se sakht mohabbat karne wala hai
  100,9,kiya woh is waqt ko nahi jaanta ke jo ( murdy ) qabron mein hain woh bahar nikaal liye jayen ge
